'''恩蒂萨尔·埃尔赛德'''（Entisar Elsaeed）是[[埃及|埃及]]的一名律師與女權運動者<ref name=NYP>{{Cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2020/06/28/egyptian-belly-dancer-sentenced-to-prison-for-posting-racy-tiktoks/|title=Egyptian belly dancer sentenced to prison for posting racy TikTok videos|author=Kenneth Garger|date=2020-06-28|publisher=New York Post|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210904142812/https://nypost.com/2020/06/28/egyptian-belly-dancer-sentenced-to-prison-for-posting-racy-tiktoks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為開羅發展與法治基金會（{{lang-ar|مؤسسة القاهرة للتنمية والقانون}}）的創辦人，致力於遏止[[女陰殘割|女陰殘割]]、幫助[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]受害者與推廣[[性教育|性教育]]<ref name="OHCHR">
